SAPNETS is a full-fledged ERP solutions for schools to manage entire school functioning. Best part, all things are on cloud. So you can access school data from anywhere. Personalized login credential system helps in secure usage and control of each and every user accounts. For admin accounts, machine binding makes sure that admin gains access only via registered machine. The SAPNETS team is available 24/7 to help you whenever you encounter a problem or have a question about SAPNETS.
Features 
CCE Report Card Software
Accounts Management
Payroll Management
Admission Management
Reception Management
Communication System
Timetable Management*
Transport Management
Exam Management
Tuck Shop Management
Event Management
User Management
Hostel Management
Messaging(email & SMSes)
Library Management
Online Examination System
SAPNETS is an integrated cloud based school management system and sms software which focuses on excellence and evolution in the field of Education. 
